     8тЖТclass TypeCheckMemo:
     9тЖТ    """
    10тЖТ    Contains information necessary for type checkers to do their work.
    11тЖТ
    12тЖТ    .. attribute:: globals
    13тЖТ       :type: dict[str, Any]
    14тЖТ
    15тЖТ        Dictionary of global variables to use for resolving forward references.
    16тЖТ
    17тЖТ    .. attribute:: locals
    18тЖТ       :type: dict[str, Any]
    19тЖТ
    20тЖТ        Dictionary of local variables to use for resolving forward references.
    21тЖТ
    22тЖТ    .. attribute:: self_type
    23тЖТ       :type: type | None
    24тЖТ
    25тЖТ        When running type checks within an instance method or class method, this is the
    26тЖТ        class object that the first argument (usually named ``self`` or ``cls``) refers
    27тЖТ        to.
    28тЖТ
    29тЖТ    .. attribute:: config
    30тЖТ       :type: TypeCheckConfiguration
    31тЖТ
    32тЖТ         Contains the configuration for a particular set of type checking operations.
    33тЖТ    """
